[
    {
        "text": "International finance is on the precipice.",
        "startTime": 233,
        "endTime": 3229,
        "slowStartTime": 500,
        "slowEndTime": 5068
    },
    {
        "text": "The World Bank says the global economy is perilously close to falling into recession.",
        "startTime": 3378,
        "endTime": 9151,
        "slowStartTime": 5217,
        "slowEndTime": 13951
    },
    {
        "text": "War in Ukraine and the continuing effects of the pandemic...",
        "startTime": 9558,
        "endTime": 12690,
        "slowStartTime": 14487,
        "slowEndTime": 19260
    },
    {
        "text": "…mean it has significantly downgraded its expectations for this year.",
        "startTime": 12781,
        "endTime": 17220,
        "slowStartTime": 19321,
        "slowEndTime": 26055
    },
    {
        "text": "The global economy is projected to grow by just 1.7 percent in 2023.",
        "startTime": 17651,
        "endTime": 23748,
        "slowStartTime": 26627,
        "slowEndTime": 35847
    },
    {
        "text": "The slowest growth for over three decades.",
        "startTime": 23821,
        "endTime": 26223,
        "slowStartTime": 35882,
        "slowEndTime": 39559
    },
    {
        "text": "2024 isn't looking much better.",
        "startTime": 26601,
        "endTime": 29725,
        "slowStartTime": 40051,
        "slowEndTime": 44812
    },
    {
        "text": "Franziska Ohnsorge from the World Bank told us that more developed nations...",
        "startTime": 30005,
        "endTime": 34681,
        "slowStartTime": 45158,
        "slowEndTime": 52246
    },
    {
        "text": "…are on course for a particularly bad year.",
        "startTime": 34810,
        "endTime": 37199,
        "slowStartTime": 52365,
        "slowEndTime": 56024
    },
    {
        "text": "By our forecast, slowdowns in advanced economy growth...",
        "startTime": 39184,
        "endTime": 43199,
        "slowStartTime": 58926,
        "slowEndTime": 65023
    },
    {
        "text": "…are steeper than in emerging markets and developing economy growth.",
        "startTime": 43437,
        "endTime": 47081,
        "slowStartTime": 65305,
        "slowEndTime": 70846
    },
    {
        "text": "In advanced economy, the policy tightening that's currently underway...",
        "startTime": 47367,
        "endTime": 51101,
        "slowStartTime": 71200,
        "slowEndTime": 76876
    },
    {
        "text": "...is sharply weighing on growth.",
        "startTime": 52094,
        "endTime": 54009,
        "slowStartTime": 78291,
        "slowEndTime": 81238
    },
    {
        "text": "It is much necessary, much needed...",
        "startTime": 54105,
        "endTime": 56270,
        "slowStartTime": 81307,
        "slowEndTime": 84630
    },
    {
        "text": "…because inflation has turned out to be much higher for much longer...",
        "startTime": 56660,
        "endTime": 59803,
        "slowStartTime": 85140,
        "slowEndTime": 89929
    },
    {
        "text": "…than we had anticipated in even just six months ago.",
        "startTime": 59868,
        "endTime": 63439,
        "slowStartTime": 89952,
        "slowEndTime": 95383
    },
    {
        "text": "Six months ago we expected a consensus forecast.",
        "startTime": 63513,
        "endTime": 66098,
        "slowStartTime": 95419,
        "slowEndTime": 99372
    },
    {
        "text": "Expected inflation in advanced economies in 2023...",
        "startTime": 66178,
        "endTime": 70420,
        "slowStartTime": 99417,
        "slowEndTime": 105855
    },
    {
        "text": "...to be not that far off inflation targets of 2%.",
        "startTime": 70481,
        "endTime": 73708,
        "slowStartTime": 105871,
        "slowEndTime": 110787
    },
    {
        "text": "At this point, inflation is expected to be around 5%, double that.",
        "startTime": 74099,
        "endTime": 78742,
        "slowStartTime": 111299,
        "slowEndTime": 118338
    },
    {
        "text": "So, of course, central banks are tightening policy.",
        "startTime": 79067,
        "endTime": 81232,
        "slowStartTime": 118750,
        "slowEndTime": 122073
    },
    {
        "text": "Have to tighten policy more than anticipated.",
        "startTime": 81306,
        "endTime": 83983,
        "slowStartTime": 122109,
        "slowEndTime": 126200
    },
    {
        "text": "And that is weighing on growth.",
        "startTime": 84271,
        "endTime": 85923,
        "slowStartTime": 126556,
        "slowEndTime": 129109
    }
]